                                                                                                                                                        Does Automatic Enabling of Accessibility Tools Impact Website Traffic? 
                                                                                                                                                        Research Proposal 
                                                                                                                                                        4/2/21 
                                                                                                                                                        Ryan Knorr
                                                                                                                                                        ,
                                                                                                                                                        Michelle Shen
                                                                                                                                                        ,
                                                                                                                                                        Denise Ferniza
                                                                                                                                                        , Peter Morgan 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Overview 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        When adding changes to text below, please make them in red or highlight yellow - Ryan. 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Section 508 of the Rehabilitation Act was amended in 1998 requiring federal agencies to make 
                                                                                                                                                        their electronic information technology (EIT) accessible for individuals with disabilities. While the 
                                                                                                                                                        legislation applies to Federal agencies, any entity doing business with federal agencies must 
                                                                                                                                                        also follow Section 508, commonly referred to as 508 compliance. Approximately one in four 
                                                                                                                                                        adults, or around 61 million Americans, have disabilities that impact their daily activities. The six 
                                                                                                                                                        disability categories for which 508 compliance mandates accommodation are mobility, cognition, 
                                                                                                                                                        hearing, vision, independent living​,​ and self-care.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Embracement and implementation of 508 compliance standards provides millions of Americans 
                                                                                                                                                        with access to EIT. Tasks that may be otherwise difficult for a disabled person, such as 
                                                                                                                                                        navigating to important documents ​such as ​like ​online forms, requisitions, government 
                                                                                                                                                        correspondence, and policies, are made possible with ​accessible​accessibile​ity​ EIT. Disabled 
                                                                                                                                                        Americans ​suffer​ ​must navigate through ​from ​EIT ​that is ​presented ​solely​ ​primarily ​for people 
                                                                                                                                                        without disabilities​. ​;​ ​Almost all ​lacking ​website​s do not have​ ​embedded accessibility ​navigation 
                                                                                                                                                        tools​. This lack of ease in consuming EIT ​, ​they experience both ​ creates ​reduction​s​ in 
                                                                                                                                                        purchasing power in ecommerce as well as ​increases the ​bar​riers ​to entry for entrepreneurial 
                                                                                                                                                        pursuits​. ​ such as exploring markets.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        When businesses fail to account for​ the​ accessibility needs of a large portion of society, they 
                                                                                                                                                        narrow their potential customer pool. ​This ​Our ​research seeks to ascertain if lack of operability 
                                                                                                                                                        of business​’​es​ EIT lowers their website traffic, and misses positive public relations opportunities. 
                                                                                                                                                        This study targets 508 compliant business​es, ​and will engage with ​ leaders​, such as C-Suite 
                                                                                                                                                        executives and marking managers, ​ ​who have not yet implemented accessibility tools on their 
                                                                                                                                                        websites​.​, such as C-Suite Executives, and marketing managers, that ​ and ​wish to provide 
                                                                                                                                                        increased accessibility to their products or services. The primary aim of this to research is 
                                                                                                                                                        provide data that will allow ​t​o allow these ​enterprises to realize the full benefits of creating and 
                                                                                                                                                        publishing enterprise EIT that is operational with existing 508 compliance tools  
                                                                                                                                                        already on the market​.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Research Question 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Does enabling accessibility tools by default on a company’s website effect website traffic of a 
                                                                                                                                                        508-compliant business?  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        How does implementing 508 compliant tools affect a company? 
                                                                                                                                                        a.Are there adverse effects to defaulting to accessibility such as usability issues by 
                                                                                                                                                        non-disabed customers? 
                                                                                                                                                        b.How will accessibility by default effect current customer interaction? 
                                                                                                                                                        c.Is there a requirement for a PR campaign alongside accessibility by default? 
                                                                                                                                                        i.How will disabled people know that these new businesses are accessible 
                                                                                                                                                        to them?  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Null hypothesis: Enabling accessibility tools by default on websites for 508-compliant 
                                                                                                                                                        businesses does not affect website traffic​. 
                                                                                                                                                        Alternative hypothesis: Enabling accessibility tools by default on websites for 508-compliant 
                                                                                                                                                        businesses effects website traffic 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Discussion/Conclusion followup questions below (we are not addressing these in our design, 
                                                                                                                                                        but....is there a discussion/conclusion section we can stick these?): ​¶
                                                                                                                                                        Are there secondary benefits such as public perception, increased revenue, or an increase in 
                                                                                                                                                        customer retention?​¶
                                                                                                                                                        How does implementing 508 compliant tools affect a company?​¶
                                                                                                                                                        d.Are there adverse effects to defaulting to accessibility such as usability issues by 
                                                                                                                                                        non-disabed customers?​¶
                                                                                                                                                        e.How will accessibility by default effect current customer interaction?​¶
                                                                                                                                                        f.Is there a requirement for a PR campaign alongside accessibility by default?​¶
                                                                                                                                                        i.How will disabled people know that these new businesses are accessible 
                                                                                                                                                        to them? ​¶
                                                                                                                                                        ii.¶
                                                                                                                                                        iii.¶
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Data 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        We propose using website traffic data collected over a 2-year period for our analysis. Website 
                                                                                                                                                        traffic data includes: 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Number of users visiting the website daily 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Visit lengths per user 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Page popularity 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Website speed (page download speed or website access speed) 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Website bounce rate 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Popular visitor channels (referred by website or search engine) 
                                                                                                                                                        In collaboration with researchers, participants will be required to log this data for the duration of 
                                                                                                                                                        the study​.​, with quarterly data deliverables. ​ ​The researchers ​We​ propose collecting new data 
                                                                                                                                                        rather than using existing website traffic metrics ​that ​companies may already collect​. This is​,​ ​to 
                                                                                                                                                        limit unknown variables entering the research​as this way we have more ​ and all more ​control 
                                                                                                                                                        over ​the ​data collection methods, frequency, and elements for a comparative analysis. ​The 
                                                                                                                                                        researchers acknowledge that utilizing ​Although using ​existing ​business ​data​ analytics​ that 
                                                                                                                                                        companies have already collected for our control group ​would be more cost-effective,​ but due to 
                                                                                                                                                        the variability in the type, and retention ot data there is significant concern about disparate data.  
                                                                                                                                                        because our study involves individual company website traffic data, we ​A​a​nticipat​ing ​e ​that 
                                                                                                                                                        existing data from different companies may have ​formatting ​discrepancies ​that would ​need ​ing 
                                                                                                                                                        to be ​harmoniz​ation ​ed and that ​would​ also​ add another layer of uncertainty to ​data​our​ analysis. 
                                                                                                                                                        To establish a control dataset, ​this study will ​we propose​ collect​ing new ​data using the same 
                                                                                                                                                        website traffic monitoring tool ​across enterprises, at no cost to them. This will include ​a​nd 
                                                                                                                                                        collecting data points at fixed intervals that ​will be ​can be conveniently ​replicated the following 
                                                                                                                                                        year after enabling auto-on accessibility tools. 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Other data of interest that we will collect: 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Name of accessibility tool implemented for treatment group 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Name of website traffic monitoring tool 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Company/enterprise name 
                                                                                                                                                        ●Company/enterprise business sector 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Study Design 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        The goal of this project is to determine if enabling accessibility tools on a website by default 
                                                                                                                                                        influences website traffic utilizing a quantitative experiment. Participating businesses will 
                                                                                                                                                        provide or give researchers access to data on website traffic, specifically clicks, unique users, 
                                                                                                                                                        and length of time spent on the enterprises web page. We will be collecting time series data for 
                                                                                                                                                        each website we observe. Participating business will enable a in-site screen reader, implement 
                                                                                                                                                        a keyboard only focus tool, and default to voice activation.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        (i just moved this here from Data where it was) This study will target businesses with an interest 
                                                                                                                                                        in expanding their current accessibility or striving to comply with Section 508. th ​Participation 
                                                                                                                                                        will be limited to enterprises that have track, or have access to at least 12 months of specific 
                                                                                                                                                        metrics. These metrics are website traffic, concurrent users, number of impressions (​I don’t 
                                                                                                                                                        know what this means), ​website generated revenue, and customer feedback.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Specifically, participating businesses need to implement in-site accessibility tools to collect 
                                                                                                                                                        additional data for comparative analysis. This will allow the researchers and company to 
                                                                                                                                                        measure website traffic, to include the length of time on a page, unique users, and clicks.(I think 
                                                                                                                                                        this part needs to go into study design). 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Sample 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        To limit inconsistency in this research businesses that are less than five years old, are 
                                                                                                                                                        expanding/contracting, or have not reached maturity will not be studied.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Our population for this experiment will be 508-compliant companies that might be considering 
                                                                                                                                                        implementing auto-enabled accessibility tools on their websites. 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        We will use cluster sampling to identify a sample of companies representative of various 
                                                                                                                                                        business sectors, limiting to federal agencies and/or enterprises that do business with federal 
                                                                                                                                                        agencies, as these are within the purview of Section 508. These sectors include education, 
                                                                                                                                                        health care, biotechnology, information technology, energy, aerospace, and advanced 
                                                                                                                                                        manufacturing, among others.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Some ideas for limiting scope of initial research project: 
                                                                                                                                                        1.To limit the scope of ​preliminary research this research will focus on communications 
                                                                                                                                                        companies that are prime or subcontractors to the federal government. This will allow 
                                                                                                                                                        research to be conducted on businesses that are currently 508 compliant and have a 
                                                                                                                                                        vested interest in ensuring compliance.  
                                                                                                                                                        2.To limit the scope of ​preliminary research this research will focus on enterprises that 
                                                                                                                                                        provide educational services to the federal government, such as courseware, 
                                                                                                                                                        foundational education, and program of instruction. This will allow research to be 
                                                                                                                                                        conducted on businesses that are currently 508 compliant and have a vested interest in 
                                                                                                                                                        ensuring compliance.  
                                                                                                                                                        3.Other specific industries we might limit to are communications logistics, 
                                                                                                                                                        archivists/historical businesses, businesses that provide accessibility services (medical 
                                                                                                                                                        devices, prothetics, hearing aids, etc.) 
                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        First, we will email out to these companies details of our experiment ensuring to explicitly state 
                                                                                                                                                        that there is potential to drive more website traffic. We would offer free installation of 
                                                                                                                                                        accessibility tools as well as trainings on how to automatically enable these tools on a 
                                                                                                                                                        company’s website as an incentive to participate. From the companies that say they are 
                                                                                                                                                        interested in participating, we will randomly sample 100 companies that will participate in our 
                                                                                                                                                        experiment.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Variables and/or Intervention 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Types of traffic being considered: clicks, likes (where applicable), unique individuals, customer 
                                                                                                                                                        feedback, length of time spent on page.  
                                                                                                                                                        Discuss tools that can be used and what ones cannot​ ← I think we should stick to one tool to 
                                                                                                                                                        keep things simple, but we can mention other tools in the Discussion/Conclusion 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        The main variable that we will observe is website traffic. Our control group will consist of 
                                                                                                                                                        website traffic data collected from companies that do not have accessibility tools automatically 
                                                                                                                                                        enabled on their 508-compliant websites. Our treatment group will consist of website traffic data 
                                                                                                                                                        collected from companies who have auto-enabled these (relying on denise for names) tools on 
                                                                                                                                                        their websites. 
                                                                                                                                                        The intervention in this study will be having accessibility tools automatically enabled on a 
                                                                                                                                                        website iWe will compare website traffic data collected over a two-year period, collecting 
                                                                                                                                                        control group data in the first year and collecting treatment group data in the second year. .  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Statistical Methods  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        We will perform ​a ​statistical significance testing on our dataset. We propose comparing monthly 
                                                                                                                                                        website traffic data from the control group to website data from the treatment group from the 
                                                                                                                                                        corresponding month to account for naturally occurring variance in website traffic based on time 
                                                                                                                                                        of year. Assuming that website traffic data is normally ​distributed​distribution​, we propose using 
                                                                                                                                                        a Mann-Whitney U test to compare monthly data from treatment and control groups. This test 
                                                                                                                                                        assumes that observations from the treatment and control groups are independent of each 
                                                                                                                                                        other and requires ordinal data. If the Mann-Whitney test ascertains that the distributions of the 
                                                                                                                                                        treatment and control groups are not equal, we reject the null hypothesis and accept the 
                                                                                                                                                        alternative hypothesis. We will compute effect sizes and ​confidence ​intervals​test on the 
                                                                                                                                                        experiment to determine if our results are meaningful​.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Potential Risks 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        1.Data acquisition​: can companies be convinced to participate in a 2-year study? 
                                                                                                                                                        2.Are there ethical concerns about using website traffic data? I’m guessing no (since I feel 
                                                                                                                                                        like there are a lot of studies that use this metric); just putting it out there though 
                                                                                                                                                        3.Cost of Incentive, If we help companies develop their website to be 508 compliant this 
                                                                                                                                                        could be very expensive. Ensuring that companies are able to use the same website 
                                                                                                                                                        traffic tracking tools and potential overhead costs  
                                                                                                                                                        4.Ethical concern of potentially harming businesses if it turns out that enabling 508 
                                                                                                                                                        compliance decreases website visits. 
                                                                                                                                                        5.One thing to consider is the potential that website views change from month to month in 
                                                                                                                                                        the year. A way to account for this is to look at past website view data and see if there is 
                                                                                                                                                        a change from the first month to the second month and normalize the results based on 
                                                                                                                                                        this.​ I agree, but I think this should not be a potential risk since it should be a 
                                                                                                                                                        consideration in our sample design. 
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Deliverables  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        We established the timeframe to account for potential COVID-related deviations in data 
                                                                                                                                                        collection. ​We hope ​Thethe​ proposed timeframe is representative of businesses as they 
                                                                                                                                                        function free from pandemic influence, although ​it is ​we​ acknowledge​d​ ​that ​there may be ​some 
                                                                                                                                                        lingering ​economic ​effects​ that may influence website traffic​.The anticipated​ length of this study 
                                                                                                                                                        will be approximately 30 months. The​ data-collection timeline for this research design will be 2​4 
                                                                                                                                                        months ​years​ beginning October 2022. Data collection will occur from October 2022 to 
                                                                                                                                                        September 2024. The period from October 2022 to September 2023, ​is allocated​will be used to 
                                                                                                                                                        establish​ ​for ​the control dataset consisting of metrics on website traffic without implementation 
                                                                                                                                                        of accessibility tools. The next data-collecting period from October 2023 to September 2024 will 
                                                                                                                                                        be used to collect website traffic data after implementation of auto-on accessibility tools. Results 
                                                                                                                                                        will be analyzed from October 2024 to March 2025. The deliverable of this experiment will be a 
                                                                                                                                                        report that contains the results of the experiment, along with a statistical analysis that will 
                                                                                                                                                        determine whether or not auto-enabling accessibility tools makes a difference in website traffic.  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        Discussion/Conclusion  
                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                        This research will be limited in its scope due to lack of other studies of this nature that have 
                                                                                                                                                        been conducted in the past. There may be secondary effects to defaulting accessibility tools 
                                                                                                                                                        such as the effect on public perceptions, changes in revenue, and increase/decrease in 
                                                                                                                                                        customer retention. These research questions may be explored further dependent on the 
                                                                                                                                                        outcome of this study.
